---
import InnerPage from '../layouts/InnerPage.astro';
---
<InnerPage
  title="Contact Jacob | Get a Cash Offer on Your Wichita Home"
  description="Call or text (316) 368-3344 to get a cash offer on your Wichita home. No fees, no pressure. Fair offer within 24 hours."
  heroImage="/situations/contact.jpg"
  heroTitle="Get Your Cash Offer"
  heroSub="Call, text, or fill out the form. Jacob will get back to you within 24 hours. No pressure, no obligation."
>

  <style>
    .contact-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 20px; margin: 28px 0; }
    .contact-card { background: #f3f5f8; border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px; border: 1px solid #e0e8f0; }
    .contact-card .c-icon { font-size: 2rem; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .contact-card h3 { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1a82d8; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .contact-card p { font-size: 14.5px; color: #555; margin: 0; }
    .contact-card a { color: #e87122; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; font-size: 1.1rem; }
    @media(max-width:600px){ .contact-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }
    .form-placeholder-box {
      background: white; border: 2px dashed #cce8ff;
      border-radius: 16px; padding: 48px 32px;
      text-align: center; margin: 28px 0;
    }
    .form-placeholder-box p { color: #888; font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .form-placeholder-box a { color: #e87122; font-weight: 800; font-size: 1.3rem; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>

  <h2>Reach Jacob Directly</h2>
  <div class="contact-grid">
    <div class="contact-card">
      <div class="c-icon">📞</div>
      <h3>Call or Text</h3>
      <p>Best way to reach us — Jacob answers his own phone.</p>
      <a href="tel:3163683344">(316) 368-3344</a>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-card">
      <div class="c-icon">📍</div>
      <h3>Service Area</h3>
      <p>Wichita, Derby, Mulvane, Haysville, Andover, Augusta, El Dorado, and all surrounding Sedgwick County communities.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-card">
      <div class="c-icon">⚡</div>
      <h3>Response Time</h3>
      <p>Cash offer delivered within 24 hours. Most calls returned same day.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="contact-card">
      <div class="c-icon">🗓</div>
      <h3>Availability</h3>
      <p>We're available 7 days a week, 8am–8pm. Reach out whenever it's convenient for you.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>Submit Your Address</h2>
  <div class="form-placeholder-box">
    <p>📋 Online form coming soon</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom:20px">In the meantime, the fastest way to get your offer is a quick call:</p>
    <a href="tel:3163683344">(316) 368-3344</a>
  </div>

  <h2>What Happens Next</h2>
  <div class="steps-list">
    <div class="step-row">
      <div class="step-circle">1</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>We Have a Quick Conversation</h3>
        <p>Tell us about the property — address, condition, your timeline. Takes about 5 minutes.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-row">
      <div class="step-circle">2</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>We Make You an Offer</h3>
        <p>Based on real market data. We'll walk you through how we arrived at the number.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="step-row">
      <div class="step-circle">3</div>
      <div class="step-body">
        <h3>You Decide on Your Own Terms</h3>
        <p>No pressure, no expiration clock. Take the offer, decline it, or ask questions. We're here either way.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</InnerPage>
